original_title: AKB48グループリクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2017
overview: The AKB48 Group Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2017 (AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2017) was held from January 21 to January 22, 2017 at Tokyo Dome City Hall. Fans made their voices heard by voting for their favorite AKB48/SKE48/NMB48/HKT48/NGT48/SDN48 original songs.
title: AKB48 Group Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2017
